OL,7,FA teenager is cycling 335 miles to the
OL,8,FNetherlands to raise money in memory
OL,9,Fof his best friend who died from
OL,10,Fcancer.
OL,12,FLayton Cawthorn, 14, is taking on the
OL,13,FLondon to Amsterdam challenge for,
OL,14,Fwhere his friend Daisy Bull was cared
OL,15,Ffor.
OL,17,FDaisy was told she had a tumour in her
OL,18,Fright kidney in 2021. She recovered
OL,19,Ffrom cancer three times but passed
OL,20,Faway with her patents by her side on
OL,21,F21 December last year.
