OL,7,FLayton, from , signed up for the
OL,8,Fcharity cycle ride before his friend's
OL,9,Fdeath but has decided to carry on and
OL,10,Fdo the bike ride for The Children's
OL,11,FHospital Charity in her honour.
OL,13,FLayton said: "I just keep thinking
OL,14,F(of) all the tough moments she had.
OL,16,F"I've got to get through with her. I'm
OL,17,Falways by her side and I always will
OL,18,Fbe. I said that to her when she was
OL,19,Fstill here. I'll always be there for
OL,20,Fher."
