OL,7,FLayton said he asked Daisy's family if
OL,8,Fthey still wanted him to take on the
OL,9,Fchallenge and is pleased to have their
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,F"I'm excited because Daisy's family is
OL,13,Fsuper proud of me from day one when I
OL,14,Fstarted the running to now when she's
OL,15,Fpassed away," he said.
OL,17,FLayton is the youngest cyclist take on
OL,18,Fthe challenge and has been busy
OL,19,Ftraining in preparation before it
OL,20,Fstarts in June.
