OL,7,F"I've been doing training when I get
OL,8,Fhome from school straight on the bike
OL,9,Ffor a couple of hours with my mum.
OL,11,F"On weekends we do big ones like forty
OL,12,For fifty (miles). A couple of weeks
OL,13,Fago we did a 78 miler," he added.
OL,15,FThe fundraiser is not the first Layton
OL,16,Fhas taken on in Daisy's name.
