OL,7,FHe began when Daisy was first
OL,8,Fdiagnosed, running two kilometres
OL,9,Fevery day for 109 days which was the
OL,10,Flength of her initial chemotherapy
OL,11,Ftreatment.
OL,13,FHe raised over #7,400 for Daisy and
OL,14,Fthe Haematology and Oncology ward at
OL,15,FSheffield Children's.
OL,17,FDuring Daisy's treatment Layton asked
OL,18,Fwhat helped Daisy what helped her
OL,19,Fafter chemotherapy and was told "ice
OL,20,Fpops help her throat."
