OL,7,FHe then asked his family to write to
OL,8,FAlfresco, the company who supply Mr
OL,9,FFreeze ice pops, and they agreed to
OL,10,Fprovide these for the children and
OL,11,Fyoung people on the ward.
OL,13,FHe said: "I got my mum to write to Mr
OL,14,FFreeze ice pops. They got me a three
OL,15,Fyear contract for all the wards all
OL,16,Fthe children's wards and I had loads
OL,17,Fof ice pops just to help other
OL,18,Fchildren like Daisy."
