OL,7,FCheryl Davidson from the Children's
OL,8,FHospital Charity said all the money
OL,9,Fthat Layton fundraises will go towards
OL,10,Fthe haematology and oncology ward at
OL,11,Fthe hospital.
OL,13,F"There's not enough words really he's
OL,14,Fsuch an impressive and brave young
OL,15,Fman," she said.
OL,17,F"For the tender 14, everything that
OL,18,Fhe's doing for children at the
OL,19,Fhospital and for Daisy's legacy is
OL,20,Ffantastic.
